{"type":"message","id":"36eeb942","parentId":"5ab51e88","timestamp":"2026-06-11T03:10:04.111Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-06-11 11:10:03 GMT+8] Exec failed (calm-com, code 1) :: 登录检查失败: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Thursday, June 11th, 2026 — 11:10 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-11 03:10 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781147404108}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f3d3830","parentId":"36eeb942","timestamp":"2026-06-11T03:10:10.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the heartbeat file first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ffa42abd448244cf8d3ad398","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781147404110}}
{"type":"message","id":"291e5dad","parentId":"6f3d3830","timestamp":"2026-06-11T03:10:10.814Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ffa42abd448244cf8d3ad398","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781147410812}}
{"type":"message","id":"39e09cbb","parentId":"291e5dad","timestamp":"2026-06-11T03:10:47.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前时间是 2026-06-11 11:10 (周四，工作日)，属于工作日 9:30-11:30 上午工作时段。\n\n需要检查喝水提醒时间点（10:30 附近），现在是 11:10，已经过了 10:30 但还没到 11:30，所以应该提醒喝水。\n\n不过错误信息显示\"calm-com, code 1 :: 登录检查失败: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)\"，这是某个后台任务的错误。我只看到了这个心跳错误，不涉及用户主动任务。\n\n按照 HEARTBEAT.md 规则，现在是 11:10，在工作时段（9:30-11:30），不需要提醒喝水（10:30 已过）。\n\n\n11:10 已过 10:30 喝水提醒时间点，不需要提醒。\n\n错误信息来自 calm-com，但这是后台任务失败，不影响心跳检查规则。既然在工作时段且不需要提醒，我应该回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781147410815}}
